Start
/ channel.migrate on a Session-shaped channel (Goal-backed) returns a
/ MigrationEnvelope carrying name, role, direction, config snapshot.
- set %targetIdentity% = 'peer'
- set channel "chat" call ChatGoal
- migrate channel "chat" to %targetIdentity%, write to %envelope%
- assert %envelope% is not null
- assert %envelope.Name% equals 'chat'
